         <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Finally, we were able to get back on the property on Friday, and when we first arrived at the property, it's very difficult to tell you my emotions, my thoughts, and everything because this was my baby. I had birthed it, and to see the destruction was probably one of the worst war scenes I've probably have ever seen.</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
